valid proof that ICTU Real Estate Services is either accredited or recognized by the Bangko Sentral ng Pilipinas as an independent property appraiser or as a professional association of appraisers;
valid proof of negotiation conducted by the Municipality and the land owner in order for the Audit Team to determine how the purchase price was arrived;
duly approved subdivision plan, since the lot acquired by the Municipality is part of an undivided portion of a parcel of land; and
written justification why there was a payment of transfer tax- surcharge and penalty amounting to ₱28,000.00.

