Furnish the approved SEF Budget to the Municipal Accountant, and Municipal Treasurer within seven days from its approval;
Request the quarterly SEF Utilization report from the Municipal Accountant as prescribed in the circular;
Submit the quarterly SEF Utilization report to DepEd CO, and furnish copy the Sangguniang Bayan, DBM IX and DILG IX not later than 20th day after the end of the quarter and for the annual report not later than the 15th day of February of the following year; and
Timely post the SEF Utilization report in the Full Disclosure Website, and their Bulletin Board.

